title: Bedroom with Private Full Bath Home
posting_body: ['This beloved, unique home and incredible garden is available for new rental!', 'Lots of love and purposeful upgrades have gone into the house, along with years of tending to its earth, creating the sense of a beautifully secluded oasis in the middle of the city.', " Situated in the heart of Longfellow, a coveted Minneapolis neighborhood, this home's location boasts all of the following: walking distance to Lake Street and Minnehaha businesses; one block off the Greenway; less than a mile from the Mississippi River; and a few blocks from the Light-rail.", 'The majority of the lot gets full south-facing sun; perfect for the added benefit of solar panels.', 'The food-producing garden includes a custom potting shed, greenhouse, pirate ship, and is a pollinator-friendly haven!', 'The interior highlights include a walk-in cedar closet, a custom built library/office, a workspace in the basement, and a Star Wars themed bathroom to name a few.', "If you're interested in our adverts, provide me your number so I can contact you."]
